Nomura’s Head of Asia-Pacific Debt Syndicate Mayes Leaves Bank

-- B y   S h e l l e y   S m i t h
-- 
2011-04-13T02:18:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-13/nomura-s-head-of-asia-pacific-debt-syndicate-mayes-leaves-bank.html
Nomura’s head of fixed-income
syndicate in the Asia-Pacific region has left the company, bank
spokeswoman Rosie Slater confirmed today.  Dermot Mayes, who was based in  Hong Kong , left his job this
week, Slater said. Mayes’ departure was reported earlier by
EuroWeek Asia.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Shelley Smith in Hong Kong at 
 ssmith118@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
